    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it was brand new. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like a dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
