    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied at delivery. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seating surfaces are supple and free of any creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians. The alloy wheels are flawless, without a hint of curb rash, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that truly defies its age and mileage.",
      "price": 48500.0,
